#: selfdrive/ui/sunnypilot/layouts/settings/visuals.py:44
msgid ""
"A beautiful rainbow effect on the path the model wants to take. It does not "
"affect driving in any way."
msgstr ""
"在模型规划的行驶路径上呈现出美观的彩虹效果.该效果不会以任何方式影响驾驶."

#: selfdrive/ui/sunnypilot/layouts/settings/visuals.py:62
msgid ""
"A chime and on-screen alert will play when the traffic light you are waiting "
"for turns green and you have no vehicle in front of you.<br>Note: This chime "
"is only designed as a notification. It is the driver's responsibility to "
"observe their environment and make decisions accordingly."
msgstr ""
"当你等待的交通信号灯变绿且前方无车辆时,系统会响起提示音并在屏幕上显示提醒."
"<br>注：该提示音仅作为通知用途,驾驶员有责任观察周边环境并据此做出决策."

#: selfdrive/ui/sunnypilot/layouts/settings/visuals.py:70
msgid ""
"A chime and on-screen alert will play when you are stopped, and the vehicle "
"in front of you start moving.<br>Note: This chime is only designed as a "
"notification. It is the driver's responsibility to observe their environment "
"and make decisions accordingly."
msgstr ""
"当你处于停车状态且前方车辆开始行驶时,<br>系统会响起提示音并在屏幕上显示提醒."
"<br>注：该提示音仅作为通知用途,<br>驾驶员有责任观察周边环境并据此做出决策."

