#: selfdrive/ui/layouts/settings/toggles.py:162
msgid ""
"sunnypilot defaults to driving in chill mode. Experimental mode enables "
"alpha-level features that aren't ready for chill mode. Experimental features "
"are listed below:<br><h4>End-to-End Longitudinal Control</h4><br>Let the "
"driving model control the gas and brakes. sunnypilot will drive as it thinks "
"a human would, including stopping for red lights and stop signs. Since the "
"driving model decides the speed to drive, the set speed will only act as an "
"upper bound. This is an alpha quality feature; mistakes should be expected."
"<br><h4>New Driving Visualization</h4><br>The driving visualization will "
"transition to the road-facing wide-angle camera at low speeds to better show "
"some turns. The Experimental mode logo will also be shown in the top right "
"corner."
msgstr ""
"阳光领航默认以舒适模式行驶.实验模式会启用暂不适用于舒适模式的Alpha级功能,\n"
"实验性功能如下：\n"
"【端到端纵向控制】\n"
"由驾驶模型控制油门和刹车,阳光领航将按照人类驾驶逻辑行驶,包括在红灯和停车标志"
"前停车.\n"
"由于行驶速度由驾驶模型自主决定,设定速度仅作为最高限速.此功能为Alpha级质量,可"
"能存在误差.\n"
"【全新驾驶可视化界面】\n"
"低速行驶时,驾驶可视化界面会切换至朝前的广角摄像头画面,以便更清晰展示转弯场"
"景.\n"
"同时右上角会显示实验模式标识."

#: selfdrive/ui/layouts/settings/device.py:165
msgid ""
"sunnypilot is continuously calibrating, resetting is rarely required. "
"Resetting calibration will restart sunnypilot if the car is powered on."
msgstr ""
"阳光领航持续进行校准,极少需要手动重置.若车辆处于通电状态,重置校准会重启"
"sunnypilot."

#: selfdrive/ui/layouts/settings/firehose.py:12
#: selfdrive/ui/mici/layouts/settings/firehose.py:21
msgid ""
"sunnypilot learns to drive by watching humans, like you, drive.\n"
"\n"
"Firehose Mode allows you to maximize your training data uploads to improve "
"openpilot's driving models. More data means bigger models, which means "
"better Experimental Mode."
msgstr ""
"openpilot 通过观察人类（例如您）的驾驶来学习.\n"
"Firehose 模式可让您最大化上传训练数据,以改进 openpilot 的驾驶模型.更多数据意"
"味着更大的模型,也意味着更好的实验模式."

#: selfdrive/ui/layouts/settings/toggles.py:187
